  schema:name "Sheaf" ;
  schema:description "A sheaf is a [presheaf](./presheaf.md) — an assignment of data to each object of a [site](./site.md) — that satisfies the [sheaf condition](./sheaf-condition.md): compatible local data can be uniquely glued into global data." ;
